Author: wdymitsnot2007
Text: God this is what I do. Because I’m so young (14) I trigger myself with pictures of me just as I was hitting puberty (12) but before I got the puberty weight gain. It sucks because I’ve had dysmorphia since I was four and at the time I didn’t realise that I was a literal stick

Text: In this exact same situation right now
